    "name": "Eight Dragons 2",
    "steam_appid": 2132260,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eight Dragons 2</strong> is an action-packed arcade <strong>beat-'em-up</strong> for up to <strong>8 players</strong>. Build your crew and take on the gangs that rule the city in this side-scrolling brawler, fighting waves of unforgiving enemies in a vibrant 2D world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/1504bd0b6691af85b3f8b79666065b11.poster.avif?t=1767956869\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/1504bd0b6691af85b3f8b79666065b11.webm?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/1504bd0b6691af85b3f8b79666065b11.mp4?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ultimate 8 Player Co-op</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join forces in local or online multiplayer for chaotic cooperative gameplay, coordinating epic takedowns in increasingly huge battles. Mix and match up to eight players in any combination of local or online players across all platforms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/6389162b673f7b3ecbcafde95d49f5b5.poster.avif?t=1767956869\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/6389162b673f7b3ecbcafde95d49f5b5.webm?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/6389162b673f7b3ecbcafde95d49f5b5.mp4?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Retro Arcade Action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into classic side-scrolling combat, blending nostalgic arcade vibes with modern mechanics and stunning pixel graphics. Drop-in/drop-out multiplayer, with progress automatically saved as you play so your effort is never wasted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/457ef873bf4c5466470f1215d279ef53.poster.avif?t=1767956869\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/457ef873bf4c5466470f1215d279ef53.webm?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/457ef873bf4c5466470f1215d279ef53.mp4?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dynamic Characters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from <strong>8 unique characters</strong>, each with distinct fighting styles and <strong>special moves</strong>. Learn their strengths and weaknesses and play as whichever best suits your style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/79b11d05979cb7bee7b1a00b9dcb10f0.poster.avif?t=1767956869\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/79b11d05979cb7bee7b1a00b9dcb10f0.webm?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/79b11d05979cb7bee7b1a00b9dcb10f0.mp4?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solo Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even playing a solo game you don't have to take on your enemies all by yourself. Recruit fighters to join your team - you never have to fight alone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/25859fb9bb60268e8b80c08a7ed67dee.poster.avif?t=1767956869\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/25859fb9bb60268e8b80c08a7ed67dee.webm?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/25859fb9bb60268e8b80c08a7ed67dee.mp4?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Thrilling Environments</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight through four diverse districts, from neon-lit streets to gritty slums, crushing <strong>enemies</strong> and brutal bosses with fists or improvised weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/3437a2e827e2370568b22f758d2767dd.poster.avif?t=1767956869\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/3437a2e827e2370568b22f758d2767dd.webm?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/3437a2e827e2370568b22f758d2767dd.mp4?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Classic Side-Scrolling Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smash through enemies in vibrant 2D pixel art, with intuitive controls for any controller or keyboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/1c1e8f486098bde6363cecf6c60f0e53.poster.avif?t=1767956869\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/1c1e8f486098bde6363cecf6c60f0e53.webm?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/1c1e8f486098bde6363cecf6c60f0e53.mp4?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose Your Path</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way around the city or test your skills and go straight for the final boss - the choice is yours!<strong>  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/ca7e905e843ddd9c70f73cbba2764a97.poster.avif?t=1767956869\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/ca7e905e843ddd9c70f73cbba2764a97.webm?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/ca7e905e843ddd9c70f73cbba2764a97.mp4?t=1767956869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the chaos of massive battles through the streets as you fight to reclaim them, solo or with your crew!<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras/9479e99937728f53e5b923b08d0d51da.avif?t=1767956869\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132260/extras_big/9479e99937728f53e5b923b08d0d51da.avif?t=1767956869 width=800 height=566 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Eight Dragons 2: Fight alone. Fight together. Fight everybody!</i></p>",
